data.description: You do not want to miss this Florida dream home. This 4 bedroom 2 bathroom home (plus a large office/ flex space.) Located in the highly desirable St. Augustine Shores! Situated on the golf course, the views are so peaceful! This home features a super open floor plan with lots of natural light! Updated kitchen features such as  luxury cabinets, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances including a gas range and hood, and hideaway refrigerator! Master bedroom features his and her closets, large walk in shower. The  French doors in the living area boasts access to the spacious screened in back porch, and offers a yard that will  give you plenty of room for a pool and of views of the golf course. This community also offers RV/Boat storage, a clubhouse with activities, large community pool, fishing pier and playground with very low HOA fees
